\end{center}

Figure 4. The total and partial density of states of the V-M" (3d metal elements: $\mathrm{Cr}, \mathrm{Mn}, \mathrm{Fe}, \mathrm{Co}$, and Ni) co-doped $\mathrm{BaTiO}_{3}$. The black dashed line indicates the position of the Fermi level.\\
\includegraphics[max width=\textwidth, center]{2023_09_22_63a752c620bbc784200cg-06_1822_2410_273_1783}

